                        <interp inst="t18660108-name-159" type="given" value="FREDERICK"></interp>FREDERICK SWANSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am cashier to Allen, Harrison, and Co., Manches<lb></lb>ter—on 12th July I paid the prisoner 18<hi rend="italic">l</hi>., as the traveller of the Plumbago Company—this is his receipt (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>).</p>
